Class BtMetaInfoData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inchok.aria2.BtMetaInfoData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class BtMetaInfoData
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The bit torrent meta info data retrieved from ".torrent" file. To get these data, call DownloadHandle.getBtMetaInfoData().
    Version:
    Version 1.0
    Author:
    inCHOK
